snippet.title: Cursed Despair | Co-op Horror Game | Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Cursed Despair is a psychological horror game designed for 2-4 players.

Prepare for a journey into despair! In a map brimming with secrets that will send shivers down your spine, navigate this maze-like, intricate building with your friends. But beware; you may get lost and find yourself alone in the darkness.

Take a look. You can go to the steam page by clicking the link below and buy the game immediately. You can dive into this horror experience right away.

This game is developed using Unreal Engine 5.

SteamPage:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2834580/Cursed_Despair/
